<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id8ea73dee-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6" identifier="/us/usc/t22/s268c"><num value="268c">§ 268c.</num><heading> Limitation on expenditure of funds for compensation of International Boundary Commissioner to actual hours worked</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Funds appropriated on and after <date date="1996-09-30">September 30, 1996</date>, or otherwise made available under this Act or any other Act may be expended for compensation of the United States Commissioner of the International Boundary Commission, United States and Canada, only for actual hours worked by such Commissioner.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id8ea73def-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6">(<ref href="/us/pl/104/208/dA/tI/s101/a/tIV/s403">Pub. L. 104–208, div. A, title I, § 101(a) [title IV, § 403]</ref>, <date date="1996-09-30">Sept. 30, 1996</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/110/3009">110 Stat. 3009</ref>, 3009–54.)</sourceCredit>
